# Documentation

- Keep user-facing docs concise. When changing architecture or dependencies, add/update an ADR under `docs/decisions`.
- Update the **Roadmap** and **Sprint** docs when scope changes affect delivery.
- Prefer examples over prose; include snippets and command blocks.
